hopobject.body: I'm sorry, I didn't catch your name levitra 20 mg precio farmacia Congress has the power of the purse. Tuesday was the 226th anniversary of the day in 1787 when the founding fathers approved the Constitution. Article I of the Constitution gives Congress, not the president, the responsibility to appropriate money. At the risk of a using a muddled sports metaphor, the ball is in Congress' court and it's time for House Republicans to step up to the plate.
